===Noun===
'''dysentery''' (''plural'' '''dysenteries''')

# {{pathology}} Inflammation of the [[intestine]]s, especially the [[colon]],  characterised by pain in the [[abdomen]], severe [[diarrhea]] and often with blood in the [[faeces]].

